&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://medium.com/@umarquez_mx/16-100-100daysofc0d3-eef81cd44afb&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow noreferrer&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;[&lt;sup&gt;16&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;frasl;&lt;sub&gt;100&lt;/sub&gt;] — Escalado de imágenes mediante interpolación de vecinos cercanos | Image scaling applying nearest neighbor interpolation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
